function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)
	local idServerProp = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(tServerProps[Hydra.ActorGetSNOName(idActorSpawned)], idActorSpawned, false, 0, 0)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idServerProp, EG_FADE_IN)
	Hydra.Wait(1.5)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idActorSpawned)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idServerProp)
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	
	if bCurrentlyFailing then
		return
	end
	
	local sActorTrap = Hydra.ActorGetSNOName(idActorKilled)
	local bCorrect = false
	
	if sActorTrap == tTraps[nPuzzleProgress] then
		bCorrect = true
		Hydra.ActorPlaySound(ID_PUZZLE_TRAPS[nPuzzleProgress], SFX_SUCCESS)
		Hydra.BuffRemove(POWER_TRAP_LOOK_OVERRIDE, "LOOK_OVERRIDE", ID_PUZZLE_TRAPS[nPuzzleProgress])
		nPuzzleProgress = nPuzzleProgress + 1
		
		if nPuzzleProgress == 4 then
			Hydra.EventSendToActor("PUZZLE_COMPLETE", idSelf, idSelf)
		end
	end
	
	if not bCorrect then
		failed()
	end
end

function Start(szScopedGroup, PrefabID)

	Hydra.Wait(4)
	
	for i = 1, #tTrapsToRespawn do
		local idTrap = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(tTrapsToRespawn[i]["sActor"], tTrapsToRespawn[i]["ptSpawn"], tTrapsToRespawn[i]["pfSpawn"], false, 0, 0)
		Hydra.ActorAddToPrefabScopedGroup(idTrap, "SMP_Gizmos")
		Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(POWER_TRAP_LOOK_OVERRIDE, "LOOK_OVERRIDE", idTrap)
		Hydra.ActorDisable(idTrap)
	end
	
	Hydra.ActorPlaySound(idSelf, "Play_QUE_CapturePoint_PressurePlate_Release")
	
	bCurrentlyFailing = false
	
end

function Start(idActorDamager, idActorDamaged)
	
	local bDidDamageParticipant = false
	
	for i, playerID in pairs(Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()) do
		if playerID == idActorDamaged then
			bDidDamageParticipant = true
			break
		end
	end
	
	if bDidDamageParticipant then
		failed()
	end
end

unk_c47e01a.value:
local function failed()
	if not bCurrentlyFailing then
		bCurrentlyFailing  = true
		
		for i = nPuzzleProgress, 1, -1 do
			Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(POWER_TRAP_LOOK_OVERRIDE, "LOOK_OVERRIDE", ID_PUZZLE_TRAPS[i])
		end
		
		nPuzzleProgress = 1
		
		for i, actorID in pairs(Hydra.ActorsInPrefabScopedGroup("SMP_Gizmos")) do
			Hydra.ActorKill(actorID)
		end
	end
end

unk_993f312.value:
tTraps = {ACTOR_TRAP_COLD, ACTOR_TRAP_FIRE, ACTOR_TRAP_LIGHTNING, ACTOR_TRAP_POISON, ACTOR_TRAP_SHADOW}
tServerProps = 
	{
	[ACTOR_TRAP_COLD] = ACTOR_TRAP_COLD_SP,
	[ACTOR_TRAP_FIRE] = ACTOR_TRAP_FIRE_SP,
	[ACTOR_TRAP_LIGHTNING] = ACTOR_TRAP_LIGHTNING_SP,
	[ACTOR_TRAP_POISON] = ACTOR_TRAP_POISON_SP,
	[ACTOR_TRAP_SHADOW] = ACTOR_TRAP_SHADOW_SP
	}
local tMarkers = {ID_MARKER_1, ID_MARKER_2, ID_MARKER_3}
local nTrapTypes = #tTraps

ID_PUZZLE_TRAPS = {}
tTrapsToRespawn = {}
FYShuffle(tTraps)

for i = 1, #T_TRAP_LOCATIONS do
	local ptSpawn = Hydra.ActorGetPosition(T_TRAP_LOCATIONS[i])
	local pfSpawn = Hydra.ActorGetFacing(T_TRAP_LOCATIONS[i])
	local nWrappedIndex = (i - 1) % nTrapTypes + 1
	local idTrap = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(tTraps[nWrappedIndex], ptSpawn, pfSpawn, false, 0, 0)
	Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(POWER_TRAP_LOOK_OVERRIDE, "LOOK_OVERRIDE", idTrap)
	Hydra.ActorAddToPrefabScopedGroup(idTrap, "SMP_Gizmos")
	
	tTrapsToRespawn[i] = {}
	tTrapsToRespawn[i]["ptSpawn"] = ptSpawn
	tTrapsToRespawn[i]["pfSpawn"] = pfSpawn
	tTrapsToRespawn[i]["sActor"] = tTraps[nWrappedIndex]
	
	if i %  nTrapTypes == 0 then
		FYShuffle(tTraps)
	end
end

FYShuffle(tTraps)

for i = 1, 3 do
	local idTrap = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(tTraps[i], tMarkers[i], false, 0, 0)
	Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(POWER_TRAP_LOOK_OVERRIDE, "LOOK_OVERRIDE", idTrap)
	ID_PUZZLE_TRAPS[i] = idTrap
	Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idTrap, true)
end

nPuzzleProgress = 1
bCurrentlyFailing = false
